rows.label: qst701601_msg0001
rows.name:
Please! Let me eat the
specialty dish here!

rows.label: qst701601_msg0002
rows.name:
Maulton-san... You've been staying
here for so long, but I can't make
anything decent anymore...

rows.label: qst701601_msg0003
rows.name: I told you before, didn't I?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0004
rows.name:
I came from Superbia to
learn about delicious food.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0005
rows.name:
I want to eat the specialty dish of the
most famous restaurant in Iira and bring
back the secret of its deliciousness!

rows.label: qst701601_msg0006
rows.name:
Even though Iira is in
danger, I'm sticking around
without running away!

rows.label: qst701601_msg0007
rows.name:
You could at least make
it for me once, right?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0008
rows.name:
Even if you say so, what's
impossible is impossible...

rows.label: qst701601_msg0009
rows.name: Hey, why is it impossible?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0010
rows.name: Laura-sama, Adel-sama...

rows.label: qst701601_msg0011
rows.name:
My father and mother, whom I left
behind in my hometown of Porton
Village, have passed away...

rows.label: qst701601_msg0012
rows.name:
I'm so sad... It's all I can
do to get through each day.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0013
rows.name: That is... hard...

rows.label: qst701601_msg0014
rows.name:
But does that mean you can
keep serving such bad food?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0015
rows.name:
...It's still better than
Superbian food, isn't it?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0016
rows.name: Well, that's true, but...

rows.label: qst701601_msg0017
rows.name: Hugo... Is Superbian food bad?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0018
rows.name:
W-Well... It seems to be
generally thought of that way.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0019
rows.name: I don't think that's the case, but...

rows.label: qst701601_msg0020
rows.name:
I'm not a fan... I much
prefer Shin's cooking.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0021
rows.name: Naturally.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0022
rows.name: Naturally...?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0023
rows.name:
My story might sound selfish,
but are you going to keep
on like this forever?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0024
rows.name:
Even though the taste is
getting worse, customers
are still coming every day.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0025
rows.name:
Isn't it a chef's job to
somehow look forward and
cook for such customers?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0026
rows.name: But...

rows.label: qst701601_msg0027
rows.name: That's it!

rows.label: qst701601_msg0028
rows.name:
Kozel... I know it's hard,
but won't you let me create
an opportunity for you?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0029
rows.name: What is it?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0030
rows.name: How about we hold a cooking contest?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0031
rows.name: That's a great idea!

rows.label: qst701601_msg0032
rows.name:
I'll put up the prize money.
Shall we book the inn for it?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0033
rows.name: The Adel Cup, is it?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0034
rows.name: That's a bit embarrassing...

rows.label: qst701601_msg0035
rows.name:
Be that as it may, the judges will
be myself, Hugo... and also...

rows.label: qst701601_msg0036
rows.name:
Let me be a judge too. It's
a great opportunity to learn
about delicious food.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0037
rows.name: Of course.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0038
rows.name:
But in times like these, I doubt
anyone would want to participate.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0039
rows.name: There will be.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0040
rows.name:
Shin, despite his looks,
is also a good cook.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0041
rows.name: No, I'm...

rows.label: qst701601_msg0042
rows.name: Shin, please participate.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0043
rows.name:
It will help them, and I want
to see you test your skills.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0045
rows.name: ...I understand.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0046
rows.name: Good, good.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0047
rows.name:
If we ask the people of the capital,
a few of them will surely come.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0048
rows.name: Kozel, won't you participate as well?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0051
rows.name: I understand.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0052
rows.name:
I've become interested in the food
that the Paragon of Iira makes.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0053
rows.name: This is going to be fun.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0054
rows.name: Wait a minute...

rows.label: qst701601_msg0055
rows.name: What is it?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0056
rows.name: Aren't you forgetting someone?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0057
rows.name: Is it Wadatsumi?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0058
rows.name:
Wadatsumi's fish dishes
are also delicious.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0059
rows.name: It's me!!

rows.label: qst701601_msg0060
rows.name: Just you watch, Shin.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0061
rows.name: I'm going to win.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0062
rows.name: Hmph...

rows.label: qst701601_msg0063
rows.name: Ah, you just scoffed!

rows.label: qst701601_msg0064
rows.name: I'm serious!

rows.label: qst701601_msg0065
rows.name:
Well, if I'm going to participate,
I want to give it my all.

rows.label: qst701601_msg0066
rows.name:
Can we go back to the
inn and discuss it?

rows.label: qst701601_msg0067
rows.name: Of course!

rows.label: qst701601_msg0068
rows.name:
Man, I'm looking forward
to the cooking contest.
